language Essence 1.3

given w: int(1..)
given g: int(1..)
given s: int(1..)
letting nGolfers be g * s
letting Golfers be new type of size nGolfers
find sched: matrix indexed by [int(1..w), int(1..g)] of set (size s) of Golfers
such that
    and([and([and([j1 < j2 -> |sched[i, j1] intersect sched[i, j2]| = 0 | j2 : int(1..g)]) | j1 : int(1..g)])
             | i : int(1..w)])
such that
    and([and([p1 != p2 ->
              sum([sum([toInt(p1 in sched[i, j] /\ p2 in sched[i, j]) | j : int(1..g)]) | i : int(1..w)]) <= 1
                  | p2 : Golfers])
             | p1 : Golfers])

